Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Billson.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Billson (1988), 39 Ohio St. 3d 604.]

(No. D.D. 88-9 — Submitted September 8, 1988 — Decided November 2, 1988.)

T. Michael Billson is publicly reprimanded.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
